{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"61982-malar-s-big-house","title":"Malar's Big House","description":"Malar loves to build things. What will she build today?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Thirupurasundari Sevvel"],"illustrators":["Ankitha Kini"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/61982-malar-s-big-house"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/715434/size3/5613393324b2c4300bc530bb88cb1e16.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/715434/size6/5613393324b2c4300bc530bb88cb1e16.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101106/size6/00f790a6005d8d79316f20c352de0ade.jpg","text":"Today, Malar is going to build a big house!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101264/size6/3fd8eb8bc51f989ba470a5ddc77e567b.jpg","text":"“I can use these!”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101259/size6/41dff234905b14d6cf11f3b2d98b1422.jpg","text":"“My big house will be this high!” says Malar.\n“And this wide!”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101109/size6/605f471213cd148167931d98d9991cf6.jpg","text":"Malar stacks the tumblers, one over the other.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101110/size6/8b0a514aec01a0033199503d6d247ebe.jpg","text":"All the tumblers fall down.\nTung! Tang! Dhadoom!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101111/size6/adbd9138c42c15c14fbd876001e71c00.jpg","text":"Malar picks up the tumblers and tries again.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101112/size6/a980a64397d162bce33ae2c4bea0218c.jpg","text":"Tung!\nDhadoom!\nTang!\nThey fall down. Again!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101113/size6/9a2d994b9b890adfec95cfb3422237d7.jpg","text":"This time, the tumblers don’t fall. Up, up, up they go!\nMalar thinks hard.\nShe tries again.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101114/size6/a3e41dac446486caa4e48ce5dd4145b4.jpg","text":"Malar’s big, shiny house\nis almost ready.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101206/size6/9a4c8370d86c40f1e76ce461ab374d52.jpg","text":"Malar rushes to the kitchen. Everyone is busy. \n“What do you need, Malar?” asks Appa.\n\"Can you give me half a coconut, Appa? My house needs a roof.\"\n“Ah, yes! It does,” says Appa.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101117/size6/bdc9e3323c1892e0604c021696acea17.jpg","text":"“Do you like my big house, Appa?”\n“Yes, I do. This is such a lovely palace!”","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101262/size6/66f946940a701eaad74f174a6ffb6a94.jpg","text":"DABADABA-DUM! TUNG! TANG!\nWhat will Malar build next?","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101119/size6/549f49fa0f483bba8d669a28422c8f5a.jpg","text":"Build Your Own Palace\nYou will need:\n- As many paper cups as you can find\n- 1 round vessel from your kitchen\n- Crayons or colour pencils\n- 1 coconut (cut in half)\nTa-da! Your palace is ready!","words":null}]